::Magmatron::

    "You didn't have to run." Magmatron said to Bazooka and Mantella. 
"Bobertron isn't even here yet."
    "Bobertron you must report to the Lab ASAP." Magmatron said into his 
comm. "Since he isn't here yet we can start with you. You would like you keep 
you beast mode, yes?" Magmatron said to Mantella. "Anyway all you have to do 
is lie down in this chair and relax. The procedure might pinch a little."
    "Bazooka, Bobertron has picked up a signal, go and greet it for me, and 
Bazooka, remember to smile once and a while."
    Bazooka put on a really fake simile and walked out side.
    "Ready?" Magmatron said to Mantella.
